{"tid":1572211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地可唔可以唔好再用害死人組合？","createTime":"2019-09-15T15:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T15:26:38.000Z","uid":304321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0e0bd1079414dd55d71228445d7f4d7a0459a2","tid":1572211,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"話說我今日係最低消費個到做流動物資送禮勤<br />\n咁就見到好多溫馴既BB個豬咀係用緊<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">害死人組合</span></ins></strong> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tPAJYWq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtPAJYWq.png&h=7e831d2e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n作為送禮勤  我就緊係衝上去送個大禮比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbb竟然問我：「我依家用緊呢個唔得架咩？」<br />\n我：「你呢個係害死人組合，唔得架bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\nbb：「姐係點呀？」<br />\n我：「姐係會害撚死你 聽話 換左個大禮就安全架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n你地可唔可以乖乖地換左個罐佢？真係好毒架 <br />\n我求下你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有另一個傻豬bb見到我送大禮過佢時..<br />\nBB：「哦！我比返錢你丫！」<br />\n然後9秒9除低袋拎銀包出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地可唔可以唔好咁？<br />\n我送禮勤一生只係想送個禮 無他架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}